org.eclipse.rdf4j.sail.memory.model

Class MemStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.SimpleStatement
      • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.ContextStatement
        • org.eclipse.rdf4j.sail.memory.model.MemStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Statement

    public class MemStatement
extends ContextStatement
    A MemStatement is a Statement which contains context information and a flag indicating whether the statement is explicit or inferred.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
